==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Koklass
<hw>Ko"klass</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any pheasant of the genus <gen>Pucrasia</gen>. The birds of this
genus inhabit India and China, and are distinguished by having a long
central and two lateral crests on the head. Called also
<altname>pucras</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kokoon</ent>⟦br⟧
